ActYouth Criminal Justice Act
SubjectYouth Justice Services Funding Program and the Intensive Rehabilitative Custody and Supervision Program ** Contribution Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Justice, to ENTER INTO new six-year CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENTS for the fiscal years 2021-22 to 2026-27 with provinces and territories in order to continue contribution funding through the Youth Justice Services Funding Program and the Intensive Rehabilitative Custody and Supervision Program.
